metadata.name: ZiZis (GEN-Z) by Zanolino #1
metadata.description: The Zizi-team was founded by father and son art team, Philippe and Giovani Zanolino. After 5 decades of producing thousands of physical and digital artworks, they have now translated their vision into generative NFTs with the help of artBloots creator Prker. Owning a Gen-Z is the key to max Zizi utility.
